			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="#regest1">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salve, mi venerande et optime Bullingere.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="565">Constantiam</placeName> nuper, hoc est 26. augusti, cum bona Wirtempergensis principis<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="224">Ulrich</persName>, <persName ref="224">Herzog von Württemberg</persName>.</note> gratia redii, nisi quod ille malignius ęquo mihi numeravit; nam tantum non 300 aureorum iacturam feci toto illo quadriennio, quo in ipsius ditione non ferendorum laborum molestia oppressus prorsumque enectus sum.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et tamen gratias ago deo meo, quod bona conscientia illinc explicitus iam meis restituor.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Volui autem, licet occupatissimus, istuc tibi paucis indicare, quod sciam, quid amicorum meorum rumusculi iactitent, nempe irato me principe missum factum, ne desit, quod illis obiicias; nam quicquid hic peccavit princeps, non pro ira, sed pro consuetudine fecit<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Über die Entlassung <persName ref="20">Blarers</persName> am 30. Mai 1538 und deren unklare Hintergründe vgl. Martin <hi>Brecht,</hi> <persName ref="19">Ambrosius Blarers</persName> Wirksamkeit in Schwaben, in: Der <placeName ref="565">Konstanzer</placeName> Reformator <persName ref="19">Ambrosius Blarer</persName> 1492-1564. Gedenkschrift zu seinem 400. Todestag, hg. v. Bernd Moeller, <placeName ref="565">Konstanz</placeName>/Stuttgart 1964, S. 140-171, hier 166-168, und <persName ref="14">Theodor</persName> <hi>Pressel,</hi> Ambrosius Blaurer's des schwäbischen Reformators Leben und Schriften, Stuttgart 1861, S. 437f. 441-444.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic enim solet.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero autem fore, ut olim per commodam aliquam occasionem, quod nunc desidero, benigne compenset et dignam principe munificentiam exerat, quum sit in me alioqui non iniquo animo.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Commenda me clarissimis viris <persName ref="165">Pellicano</persName>, Leoni<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="114">Leo Jud</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="14">Theodoro</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="14">Theodor Bibliander</persName>.</note> ac cęteris fratribus et amicis, quorum me precibus tuis quoque additis apud Christum iuvari vehementer cupio.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te Zviccii<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="263">Johannes</persName> und <persName ref="264">Konrad Zwick</persName>.</note> cum germano meo fratre<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="20">Thomas Blarer</persName>.</note> et sorore<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="474">Margaretha Blarer</persName>.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale, mi plus quam charissime et optime frater.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="565">Constantiae</placeName>, ultima augusti anno 1538.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="19">Ambrosius Blaurerus</persName>.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="224">Heinricho</persName> Bullingero, Tiguricensis ecclesiae episcopo, domino et fratri observando atque charissimo etc.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
		</body>
